            <caption>Removing roller tappet and guides</caption>
        </figure>
        <para>Remove each roller tappet and guide from tappet bore and mark with cylinder number, valve association
            (intake or exhaust), and roller orientation. Rollers should only be re-installed so they revolve in the same
            direction as before removal.
